title: ArtyTorrent Pack 61-Ueberschall House Essentials Vocals 1-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 61-Ueberschall House Essentials Vocals 1-WAV
-------------------------------------------------------------

Part 5 of the full Ueberschall House Essentials sample disc. This pack is full of oneshot female vocal samples to be used at 130bpm.
Also included are some "special" vocal snipets which seem to have been grabbed from hit records.
According to the licence, you need to give credit to the singers if you use these samples in a commercial release, so if you have a hit with something from this pack, you&#039;d better buy the CD and give a mention to Vonda and Nina, the divas involved.

Torrent contains 13 RAR files with 300 vocal samples
----------------------------------------------------

All samples are normalized 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz.

Male vocals to follow.

Comments/thanks/requests are welcome.
